\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}$
\end_inset

, but flipped over the 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

-axis (by the 
\begin_inset Formula $-1$
\end_inset

 in the 
\begin_inset Formula $-8$
\end_inset

